This paper presents a new active learning algorithm that partitions the input space into regions and seeks a distinct predictor for each region. This algorithm has applications in machine learning, artificial intelligence, computer vision, natural language processing, and data science. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
